library(jsonlite)
library(tidyverse)
source("elattes.ls2df.R")
profile <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/profile.json")
orientacao_extracted <- extrai.orientacoes(profile)
orientacao_df <- tibble(orientacao_extracted)
orientacao_df$natureza <- gsub("[[:punct:]]", " ", orientacao_df$natureza)
orientacao_df$natureza <- gsub("monografia de conclusao de curso", "monografia de conclusao de curso\n", 
    orientacao_df$natureza)
orientacao_df$natureza <- factor(orientacao_df$natureza)
orientacao_df %>% ggplot(aes(x = fct_infreq(natureza), fill = factor(natureza))) + 
    geom_bar(position = "dodge") + theme(legend.position = "bottom", panel.grid.major.y = element_blank()) + 
    coord_flip()

profile <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/profile.json")
perfil.df.orientacoes <- extrai.orientacoes(profile)
cons529 <- perfil.df.orientacoes %>% mutate(natureza2 = if_else(trimws(natureza) == 
    "Disserta√ß√£o de mestrado", "DISS_MSTR", if_else(trimws(natureza) == "Iniciacao Cientifica" | 
    trimws(natureza) == "INICIACAO_CIENTIFICA", "INIC_CIEN", if_else(trimws(natureza) == 
    "MONOGRAFIA_DE_CONCLUSAO_DE_CURSO_APERFEICOAMENTO_E_ESPECIALIZACAO", "MONO_ESPC", 
    if_else(trimws(natureza) == "Supervisao de pos-doutorado", "SUPV_DTRD", if_else(trimws(natureza) == 
        "Tese de doutorado", "TESE_DTRD", if_else(trimws(natureza) == "Trabalho de conclusao de curso de graduacao" | 
        trimws(natureza) == "TRABALHO_DE_CONCLUSAO_DE_CURSO_GRADUACAO", "CONC_GRAD", 
        if_else(trimws(natureza) == "ORIENTACAO-DE-OUTRA-NATUREZA", "OUTR_ORIE", 
            "NA"))))))))
cons530 <- cons529 %>% select(natureza2) %>% group_by(natureza2) %>% summarize(n = n()) %>% 
    arrange(desc(n)) %>% mutate(perc = paste0(round(n/sum(n) * 100, 1), " %"))
pie <- cons530 %>% filter(n > 100) %>% ggplot(aes(x = "", y = n, fill = natureza2)) + 
    geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 1) + coord_polar("y", start = 0) + geom_text(aes(label = perc), 
    position = position_stack(vjust = 0.5), color = "white") + labs(x = NULL, y = NULL, 
    fill = NULL, title = "Volume de Orienta√ß√µes por Natureza") + theme_void() + 
    theme(axis.line = element_blank(), axis.text = element_blank(), axis.ticks = element_blank(), 
        plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, color = "#666666"))

library(jsonlite)
library(tidyverse)
source("elattes.ls2df.R")
profile <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/profile.json")
perfil.df.orientacoes <- extrai.orientacoes(profile)
oc_plot <- perfil.df.orientacoes %>% filter(grepl("_CONCLUIDA_", orientacao)) %>% 
    filter(!grepl("POS_DOUTOR", orientacao)) %>% mutate(OC = sub("ORIENTACAO_CONCLUIDA_", 
    "", trimws(orientacao))) %>% select(ano, OC) %>% group_by(ano, OC) %>% summarize(n = n())
oc_plot %>% ggplot(aes(x = as.numeric(ano), y = n), color = OC) + geom_bar(stat = "identity", 
    aes(fill = OC), position = "dodge") + geom_smooth(aes(colour = OC), method = lm, 
    formula = y ~ splines::bs(x, 3), se = FALSE) + xlab("Ano") + ylab("Quantidade") + 
    ggtitle("Orientacoes Concluidas de Mestrado e Doutorado por Ano")

library(jsonlite)
library(tidyverse)
source("elattes.ls2df.R")
advise <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/advise.json")
orient.posdoutorado.df <- ori.ls2df(advise, 6)
orient.doutorado.df <- ori.ls2df(advise, 7)
orient.mestrado.df <- ori.ls2df(advise, 8)
orient.df <- rbind(rbind(orient.posdoutorado.df, orient.doutorado.df), orient.mestrado.df)
ggplot(orient.df, aes(ano, fill = factor(natureza))) + geom_bar(stat = "count", position = "dodge") + 
    ggtitle("Natureza das Orienta√ß√µes Completas Por Ano") + theme(legend.position = "right", 
    legend.text = element_text(size = 7)) + guides(fill = guide_legend(nrow = 5, 
    byrow = TRUE, title.position = "top")) + labs(x = "Ano", y = "Quantidade") + 
    labs(fill = "Natureza") + theme_bw() + geom_text(hjust = 0.6, vjust = -0.4, size = 3, 
    color = "black", position = position_dodge(width = 0.9), stat = "count", aes(group = factor(natureza), 
        label = formatC(..count.., big.mark = ",")), check_overlap = TRUE)

Arquivo Graph

Rede de Colabora√ß√£o

source("elattes.ls2df.R")
library(tidyverse)
library(jsonlite)
library(listviewer)
library(igraph)
library(stringr)
library(tidygraph)
library(ggraph)
grafo <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/graph.json")
profile <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/profile.json")
analysis.name <- "Grande √Årea Ci√™ncias Biol√≥gicas"
docentes.sor <- grafo[["links"]][["source"]]
docentes.tar <- grafo[["links"]][["target"]]
docentes.uniq <- c(docentes.sor, docentes.tar) %>% unique()
profile2 <- list()
for (i in 1:length(docentes.uniq)) {
    profile2[[docentes.uniq[i]]] <- profile[[docentes.uniq[i]]]
}
profile <- profile2
dataFrameOrientacoes <- extrai.orientacoes(profile)
dataFramePublicacoes <- extrai.producoes(profile)
dataFrameAreasAtuacao <- extrai.areas.atuacao(profile)
dataFrameProfessores <- extrai.perfis(profile)
dataFramePerfis <- data.frame()
dataFramePerfis <- dataFrameProfessores %>% select(idLattes, nome, resumo_cv, senioridade) %>% 
    left_join(dataFrameOrientacoes %>% select(orientacao, idLattes) %>% filter(!grepl("EM_ANDAMENTO", 
        orientacao)) %>% group_by(idLattes) %>% count(orientacao) %>% spread(key = orientacao, 
        value = n), by = "idLattes") %>% left_join(dataFramePublicacoes %>% select(tipo_producao, 
    idLattes) %>% filter(!grepl("ARTIGO_ACEITO", tipo_producao)) %>% group_by(idLattes) %>% 
    count(tipo_producao) %>% spread(key = tipo_producao, value = n), by = "idLattes") %>% 
    left_join(dataFrameAreasAtuacao %>% select(area, idLattes) %>% group_by(idLattes) %>% 
        summarise(num_areas = n_distinct(area)), by = "idLattes")
wrap_strings <- function(vector_of_strings, width) {
    as.character(sapply(vector_of_strings, FUN = function(x) {
        paste(strwrap(x, width = width), collapse = "\n")
    }))
}
igraph <- g.ls2ig(grafo)
Nodes <- grafo$nodes
Links <- grafo$links
colnames(Nodes) <- c("IdLattes", "Index", "Docente")
V(igraph)$label <- paste(word(dataFramePerfis$nome, 1), word(dataFramePerfis$nome, 
    -1))
V(igraph)$orient_dout <- dataFramePerfis$ORIENTACAO_CONCLUIDA_DOUTORADO
V(igraph)$orient_mest <- dataFramePerfis$ORIENTACAO_CONCLUIDA_MESTRADO
V(igraph)$publicacao <- dataFramePerfis$PERIODICO
V(igraph)$eventos <- dataFramePerfis$EVENTO
V(igraph)$degree <- degree(igraph)
V(igraph)$betweenness <- betweenness(igraph, normalized = TRUE)
V(igraph)$closeness <- closeness(igraph, normalized = TRUE)
V(igraph)$eigen <- eigen_centrality(igraph)$vector
isolated <- which(degree(igraph) == 0)
igraph <- delete.vertices(igraph, isolated)
V(igraph)$cluster <- cluster_leading_eigen(igraph)$membership
tbl.ig <- as_tbl_graph(igraph)
tbl.ig %>% mutate(Comunidade = as.factor(group_infomap())) %>% ggraph(layout = "kk") + 
    geom_edge_link(aes(alpha = ..index.., colour = "red"), show.legend = F) + geom_node_point(aes(colour = Comunidade), 
    size = 3) + geom_node_text(aes(label = label), colour = "Black", repel = TRUE, 
    size = 3.5, vjust = 2) + ggtitle(paste("Rede de Colabora√ß√£o Entre Docentes", 
    "\n", analysis.name)) + theme_graph()

source("elattes.ls2df.R")
library(tidyverse)
library(jsonlite)
library(igraph)
library(stringr)
grafo <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/graph.json")
profile <- fromJSON("unb.biologicas/profile.json")
dataFrameOrientacoes <- extrai.orientacoes(profile)
dataFramePublicacoes <- extrai.producoes(profile)
dataFrameAreasAtuacao <- extrai.areas.atuacao(profile)
dataFrameProfessores <- extrai.perfis(profile)
dataFramePerfis <- data.frame()
dataFramePerfis <- dataFrameProfessores %>% select(idLattes, nome, resumo_cv, senioridade) %>% 
    left_join(dataFrameOrientacoes %>% select(orientacao, idLattes) %>% filter(!grepl("EM_ANDAMENTO", 
        orientacao)) %>% group_by(idLattes) %>% count(orientacao) %>% spread(key = orientacao, 
        value = n), by = "idLattes") %>% left_join(dataFramePublicacoes %>% select(tipo_producao, 
    idLattes) %>% filter(!grepl("ARTIGO_ACEITO", tipo_producao)) %>% group_by(idLattes) %>% 
    count(tipo_producao) %>% spread(key = tipo_producao, value = n), by = "idLattes") %>% 
    left_join(dataFrameAreasAtuacao %>% select(area, idLattes) %>% group_by(idLattes) %>% 
        summarise(num_areas = n_distinct(area)), by = "idLattes")
igraph <- g.ls2ig(grafo)
Nodes <- grafo$nodes
Links <- grafo$links
colnames(Nodes) <- c("IdLattes", "Index", "Docente")
V(igraph)$label <- paste(word(dataFramePerfis$nome, 1), word(dataFramePerfis$nome, 
    -1))
V(igraph)$orient_dout <- dataFramePerfis$ORIENTACAO_CONCLUIDA_DOUTORADO
V(igraph)$orient_mest <- dataFramePerfis$ORIENTACAO_CONCLUIDA_MESTRADO
V(igraph)$publicacao <- dataFramePerfis$PERIODICO
V(igraph)$eventos <- dataFramePerfis$EVENTO
V(igraph)$degree <- degree(igraph)
V(igraph)$betweenness <- betweenness(igraph, normalized = TRUE)
V(igraph)$closeness <- closeness(igraph, normalized = TRUE)
V(igraph)$eigen <- eigen_centrality(igraph)$vector
V(igraph)$cluster <- cluster_leading_eigen(igraph)$membership
grafosComunidades = fastgreedy.community(igraph)
plot(grafosComunidades, igraph, layot = layout_on_grid(igraph), vertex.size = 5, 
    vertex.label.dist = 1.9, vertex.label.cex = 0.7, edge.width = 0.9, vertex.label.color = "black", 
    vertex.label.font = 2)
